data.description: Welcome to this solid block home with a beautiful open concept in the heart of Tampa. Notable features include ROOF-12/2020, AC-2022, freshly painted inside and outside. The open concept layout conveniently connects the living room, dining room, and kitchen, making it easy to entertain friends and family. Relax with your morning coffee on the large covered carport connected to the house by a french door, perfect to enjoy surrounded by bird songs and fresh breezes. There is a top producer mango tree in the backyard, enough to enjoy yourself and give to family and friends. Completely fenced lot with your own gate and large driveway to park many cars, a truck or a boat. Don't miss the opportunity to own a beautiful property in the heart of Tampa for this price. Book you tour today!
